text: The Grumman C-2 Greyhound is an American military aircraft used for transport duties. It serve only with the United States Navy on aircraft carrier. This kind of aircraft is known as COD for Carrier Onboard Delivery. In 2020 it will be replaced by CMV-22B Osprey. == Bibliography == * * Category:Vietnam War aircraft Category:United States Navy aircraft C-2
